---
title: Tofu Burrito Bowls with Pico De Gallo and Green Onion Rice
description: Tasty tofu takes centre stage with green onion and lime rice as its co-star in this delicious dish. The fresh DIY pico de gallo makes a great extra!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-burrito-au-tofu-189f7d33.jpg
